The paper focuses on swarm-robotics applications and proposes a distributed algorithm for robust optimization at scale with local communications only. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Robotics (cs.RO), and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions applications in control and motion planning, which are relevant to the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY), and the proposed algorithm involves optimization, which is relevant to the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
